name: TheDailyStar(Bangladesh)
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, what's in the news?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
The Daily Star is the most circulated English daily newspaper of Bangladesh. It is considered as one of the most influential national newspapers.

This Alexa skill is aggregating the latest news updates from the Daily Star website. You can listen the latest news updates from Bangladesh and the world, using your Echo/Alexa enabled devices.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
